{
  "stem": "10010.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 41.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because during the war, when I was on the Aryan side with the Poles, I-- I had to-- I-- I was under assumed-- different name.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I had to act as a Polish girl, as a non-Jewish girl, as a Christian one.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But every morning, I stood before the window and I said, [NON-ENGLISH] in Hebrew, so nobody will hear-- only me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said this they cannot take away from me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- and besides, I remember this time as very lovely.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My grandmother, she was wearing a wig-- wig, naturally.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were very Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she-- oh-- Friday night, she was making the challahs and cookies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she gave me the cookies with milk every morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I loved them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then when she prepared everything, I helped her to do a little challah.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We brought it in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There used to be a cellar, because there were not Frigidaires in this time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So she put everything in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my grandfather made wine from raisins, like for Friday night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then on Friday night, we brought everything up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we had the fish, the gefilte fish, like real gefilte fish, with the gefilte things in the fish itself.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so I have lovely, lovely memories from this time from my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's why I wanted to mention.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And also, my parents-- my father was very respectful to his family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Very often-- ah-- I have to come back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My grandmother and grandfather from my mother's side, before they left for this villa in Otwock, they lived in Warsaw on a street called [NON-ENGLISH], which means lucky street.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It wasn't so lucky for them, naturally, but very often, my mother was taking us there to play, to be with the grandparents.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I-- later on, I painted a picture from this house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because I remember there were two beds with-- covered with a red plush cover.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In between this was a little-- a little cupboard with a clock, probably alarm clock, on it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it was making click-clock, click-clock all night through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when I was sleeping at the grandparents, they slept each one in a different bed, naturally.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And this-- this little table was in between.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I could hear this clock running here, and, you know, ticking all the time, and those red covers off during the daytime.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "When they put there, I always remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Now my grandfather-- my-- my father always used to take us to his father, and the children, and the stepmother.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I loved to come there, because there was a girl my age-- my father's stepsister.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And beside, I love to clean up there, because they had the-- the place of work and the-- and where they lived together-- sort of-- only divided with a divider.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There was full of sawdust in the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And when my stepmother probably didn't have time, and was untidy, so I always were tidying up, making the bed, doing the sink.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I loved doing this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother always says, oh, why do you take them there?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's so untidy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my father said, no, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He loved to come there with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we liked it, too-- me and my brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's why I came back to-- to talk about grandparents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But now coming back, you asked me what was the attitude of my parents.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As the war, you know, broke out, I remember only my-- my mother-- if nay, probably she knew that the war is inevitable.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What she did is she was a very extremely smart woman, extremely energetic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And because of her we are alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Me, and my brother, and my father survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because she decided, probably, she heard during the First World War that they didn't have textiles, and she bought textiles-- big, big pieces of textiles.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she rented a room in the same apartment that we lived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she filled up this room with textiles.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
